            <scopecontent id="aspace_0d7173a71c2f6507dc42a1350b7b6b90">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The series consists of scrapbooks containing reviews and other articles by Miles Kastendieck. For conservation reasons, the scrapbooks have been microfilmed, and researchers should consult the microfilm reels rather than the originals.</p>
               <p>Kastendieck prepared indexes for Scrapbooks 2 and 3. These indexes are available in Series II.</p>
               <p>Readers interested in Kastendieck's work as a music critic should also consult Series IV, Clippings.</p>
            </scopecontent>
